WEBVTT

00:02:26.485 --> 00:02:31.152
Volim istraživati:
kakvog je okusa riječ "kreativnost"

00:02:31.176 --> 00:02:33.190
ili "jednakost",

00:02:33.214 --> 00:02:35.660
"ljubav", "revolucija"?

00:02:35.684 --> 00:02:37.818
I što s "domovinom"?

00:02:38.358 --> 00:02:42.602
Ta riječ me ovih dana posebno muči.

00:02:42.626 --> 00:02:45.195
Na mom jeziku ostavlja sladak okus,

00:02:45.219 --> 00:02:48.605
poput cimeta, ružine vodice

00:02:48.629 --> 00:02:50.029
i zlatnih jabuka.

00:02:50.053 --> 00:02:53.251
No, ispod je neugodan,

00:02:53.275 --> 00:02:55.875
kao koprive i maslačak.

00:02:55.899 --> 00:02:59.186
Okus moje domovine, Turske,

00:02:59.210 --> 00:03:03.124
mješavina je slatkog i gorkog.